HOW TO INSTALL HOTELRES
-----------------------

1. Dependencies

* HTTP Server like Apache, lighttpd
* server executing PHP
* MySQL on any host
* read-write access to one MySQL database

2. Prerequisites

* create user for hotelres with read-write rights to one database

3. Install

* if necessary, create subdir hotelres or alike in www dir (e.g. /var/www)
* copy hotelres files to this subdir or www root dir

4. Configuration

* edit config.php to your needs, e.g. enter your MySQL credentials

5. First Steps

* access hotelres via browser, e.g. $HOSTNAME/hotelres/
* create users as needed
* create rooms available in your location



Have fun!
